Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think this is a very good thing. Freshman year is the most magical year of school because college is still fresh and new. Because of this, everybody is very eager and the dorm is very social. This leads to fun, memorable times and the formation of friendships.